reviews.body: See comments. Overall it was difficult for me to follow what was going on because a lot of the methods are really long. You have good comments outlining the logical behavior, but I would suggest breaking down the methods into smaller methods based on those comments. That would make it a lot easier to follow what's going on. :)
Reviewed `routeorch`. Overall, I find some amount of duplicate code got added due to Post action. As a suggestion, it would be good if we can try to avoid duplicates.
Routeorch part lgtm. Approving from my side.
